    "title": [
      "[Cold River, Bend]"
    ],
    "description": [
      "A gloomy shrine of hewn river stone stands aside from a bend in the frozen dirt roadway.  Tokens and trinkets litter the ground before the facade, and some have rested there long enough to meld with the dingy ice mass at the building's base.  Charms of scrimshawed bone hang from its low eaves, clacking incessantly in the gelid wind.  From within, candlelight flickers."
